00:08:09,156 --> 00:08:10,532
- Maafkan aku, Avery.
- Aduh, gawat.

184
00:08:10,616 --> 00:08:12,117
Anda tepat sasaran dalam hal itu.

185
00:08:12,201 --> 00:08:13,702
Oke, Conor, kurasa kita sudah cukup.

186
00:08:13,785 --> 00:08:15,329
Bisakah kamu membalik burger-burger ini untukku?

187
00:08:16,205 --> 00:08:17,873
Ya. Wow.

188
